05:55.480 --> 05:57.073
Hi.

05:59.526 --> 06:01.824
Hi. Thank you.

06:02.863 --> 06:04.536
You were so good.

06:06.491 --> 06:08.619
Whoo!

06:12.873 --> 06:14.500
That was so fun!

06:14.666 --> 06:16.464
Yeah, it was.

06:16.626 --> 06:19.926
Next time, can you get through
the chorus before you do your solo?

06:20.088 --> 06:21.385
Miss Thing, next time?

06:21.548 --> 06:23.642
Yeah. I have a lot more songs.

06:23.800 --> 06:27.225
