but God in our waking,

44:38.384 --> 44:41.809
God in our speaking,
God in our playing,

44:41.971 --> 44:43.564
God in our digesting,

44:43.723 --> 44:47.728
God in our working,
God in our resting.

44:47.894 --> 44:49.896
