the reverend.

47:57.833 --> 48:00.757
Oh, he's a comedian.
He was just trying to make us laugh.

48:01.295 --> 48:03.673
He's a really good man.

48:03.839 --> 48:05.841
Even goes to church sometimes. Heh.

48:06.008 --> 48:09.763
