of getting it correct.

50:00.331 --> 50:02.299
Yeah, I passed out a few times.

50:02.458 --> 50:05.086
Sure, I've had my moments.

50:05.252 --> 50:11.760
But you've never, ever, ever
seen me laying in my own vomit.

50:12.176 --> 50:13.553
Whatever you say, Mama.

50:15.095 --> 50:19.942
The fact is, I was desperate back then.

50:20.100 --> 50:22.398
Right now,
I'm trying to get myself out of here,

50:22.561 --> 50:25.565
and get myself more than
a color TV and half a room.

50:25.731 --> 50:27.028
It's okay.

50:35.407 --> 50:37.501
Well, we better go.

50:37.660 --> 50:41.710
Ms. Anderson, thanks for what looked
like could have been a great dinner.

50:44.291 --> 50:45.338
We better go.

50:48.754 --> 50:50.677
Sister!

50:50.839 --> 50:55.595
